sequenceDiagram
    participant DEV as DevClient
    participant PROXY as GitProxy
    participant AUTH as AuthService
    participant META as MetadataStore
    participant SHARD as PrimaryShard
    participant REPL as ReplicaShard
    participant HOOK as WebhookQueue

    DEV->>PROXY: git push (HTTPS/SSH)
    PROXY->>AUTH: validate token / SSH key + ACL
    AUTH-->>PROXY: ok (user, perms)
    PROXY->>META: lookup repo_id -> primary_shard
    META-->>PROXY: shard_id
    PROXY->>SHARD: forward git-receive-pack stream
    SHARD->>SHARD: validate refs, write packfile, update refs
    SHARD-)REPL: replicate (log shipping)
    SHARD-->>PROXY: push ok
    PROXY-->>DEV: refs updated

    SHARD-)HOOK: enqueue push event {repo, refs, sha}
    HOOK-)HOOK: deliver to subscribers (CI, integrations)
    Note over HOOK: triggers Actions runner pool job
